Installation instructions
Add in your composer.json

"repositories": [
        {
            "type": "vcs",
            "url": "https://github.com/JustSolve-self-serve/laravel-raccomandate"
        }
    ],


command: composer require justsolve/laravel-raccomandate:dev-main

To use this library with your app, add to your .env:
RACCOMANDATE_BASE_URI=your_base_uri
RACCOMANDATE_API_KEY=your_api_key

For test running, set your RACCOMANDATA_BASE_URI and RACCOMANDATA_API_KEY directly into the Config::set calls within the ApiCallsTest.
Otherwise, if you want to avoid exposing your testing env variables, create an .env into vendor/orchestra/testbench-core/laravel and set them there.
